occasions impacts his...

28:00.179 --> 28:03.850
Ability to provide the proper
standard of care?

28:03.883 --> 28:05.251
I'll be recommending
all three

28:05.284 --> 28:07.653
to the State Medical Board
for license suspension.

28:08.955 --> 28:11.290
**

