NASCAR drivers train in them.

28:23.369 --> 28:27.139
We use them to test our device
prototypes, and they haul ass.

28:27.173 --> 28:29.341
This is a very bad idea.

28:29.375 --> 28:31.610
If the skull base repair
doesn't hold...

28:31.643 --> 28:33.379
I could get
a subdural hematoma.

28:33.412 --> 28:36.382
Yes, we've established that.
I don't know what that means.

28:36.415 --> 28:38.885
But I do know
both of you drove
on the freeway to get here.

28:38.918 --> 28:41.888
If it's safe,
why do we have to wear...

28:41.921 --> 28:43.990
Enough negativity.
Both of you.

28:44.023 --> 28:45.557
You didn't blow off Blaize
just to go out

28:45.591 --> 28:47.559
for a walk or a nice lunch.

28:47.593 --> 28:50.729
It's time to
crank up the volume
on this day off.

28:50.763 --> 28:52.965
I don't want to
drive a go-kart.

28:52.999 --> 28:54.066
I don't believe you.
I think you do

28:54.100 --> 28:55.301
want to drive a go-kart.

28:55.334 --> 28:57.169
You just don't
want me to drive a go-kart.

28:57.203 --> 28:58.270
You know what?
I'm in.

29:01.908 --> 29:03.075
Okay.

