I'm better than fine.

32:15.467 --> 32:17.169
I'm good.

32:17.203 --> 32:20.739
**

32:20.772 --> 32:22.041
He's good.

32:22.741 --> 32:25.277
(CHUCKLING) Yes!

32:25.311 --> 32:27.513
**

32:27.546 --> 32:28.714
Come on, Shaun.

32:28.747 --> 32:30.282
(CHUCKLES)

32:30.316 --> 32:31.450
DR ANDREWS: I was wrong.

32:31.483 --> 32:32.718
From the moment we met,

32:32.751 --> 32:35.087
my defensiveness
was unprofessional

32:35.121 --> 32:37.589
and my subsequent behavior
even worse.

32:37.623 --> 32:39.958
I was not aware Dr. Lim
dosed a hospital visitor.

32:39.992 --> 32:42.928
Or that Dr. Melendez
violated a DNR.

32:42.961 --> 32:44.696
But that's my fault.

32:44.730 --> 32:48.700
Neither of them
made any attempt
to hide their actions.

32:48.734 --> 32:50.802
Because they both are totally
committed to doing

32:50.836 --> 32:52.404
whatever it takes to
provide the utmost care

32:52.438 --> 32:53.805
for their patients.

32:53.839 --> 32:58.610
Practicing medicine requires
doctors to make judgments.

32:58.644 --> 33:00.246
Not just follow rules.

33:01.447 --> 33:06.052
Two human beings
who would otherwise be dead

33:06.085 --> 33:11.990
are alive because of rules
broken by Lim and Melendez.

33:12.024 --> 33:13.625
They were doing
their jobs.

33:13.659 --> 33:14.793
They shouldn't be
punished for that.

33:14.826 --> 33:16.628
They should be applauded.

33:25.671 --> 33:28.140
I'll be notifying
the State Board
of our findings.

33:29.175 --> 33:32.010
It'll then be up
to those doctors to decide.

33:33.479 --> 33:35.847
They'll leave us bureaucrats
out of it.

33:35.881 --> 33:37.649
**

33:37.683 --> 33:39.385
See you at the hearing.

33:40.786 --> 33:42.888
**

33:56.068 --> 33:58.003
I screwed up.

33:59.171 --> 34:02.541
No, you did the right thing.
We both did.

34:02.574 --> 34:04.710
I wasn't talking about
this stupid investigation.

34:04.743 --> 34:06.145
I was talking about us.

34:08.080 --> 34:11.283
