34:11.317 --> 34:13.852
Ever since my divorce,
I can't help but think...

34:13.885 --> 34:15.421
(SIGHS)

34:16.922 --> 34:20.226
...no matter how real
this feels, it's not.

34:25.664 --> 34:27.999
I have feelings
for you.

34:28.033 --> 34:30.936
I have for a long time.

34:31.770 --> 34:33.672
And it scares me.

34:33.705 --> 34:39.044
But I don't want the night we
spent together to be our last.

34:43.682 --> 34:45.251
I feel the same way.

34:47.719 --> 34:50.522
But I'm not sure it's...
It's a good idea.

34:50.556 --> 34:54.693
Especially now
since we're both gonna
be under a microscope.

34:54.726 --> 34:56.528
Yeah, that is true.

35:00.232 --> 35:04.503
Of course, if,
for the time being,

35:04.536 --> 35:07.072
we just made sure that
Andrews and everyone else

35:07.105 --> 35:08.540
doesn't know...

35:13.245 --> 35:15.581
Interesting idea.

35:15.614 --> 35:17.616
**

35:20.819 --> 35:22.188
Good night, Neil.

35:22.221 --> 35:24.590
Good night, Audrey.

